com.yworks.yfiles.utils

Interface IListEnumerable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the contained elements.
    All Superinterfaces:
    IEnumerable<T>, Iterable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICanvasObjectGroup

    public interface IListEnumerable<T>
extends IEnumerable<T>, Iterable<T>
    An extension to the Iterable interface that allows for indexed access and retrieval of the element count. This interface is like a rudimentary read-only List.
